section_text: 1 The provisions in the Schedule to this Act shall have effect, being amendments and other provisions consequential on the re-admission of Pakistan as a member of the Commonwealth.
2 1 This Act may be cited as the Pakistan Act 1990. 2 The Pakistan Acts 1973 and 1974 are hereby repealed. 3 This Act shall be deemed to have come into force on 1st October 1989.
